('bf9e0f2c-0946-4438-b6b4-33caf0da03e8', 'How do you programmatically navigate using React Router v4?', 'In React Router v4, programmatic navigation can be done via:
1. `withRouter()` HOC (injects `history` prop)
2. `<Route>` render prop (passes `history`)
3. Context (not recommended)

